cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.IR 

The paper deals with the analysis of remote sensing images using deep learning models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a formal problem statement and a new framework for the development of deep learning models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper deals with image processing and analysis, which could also place it in cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
